&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;max-width: 100%;&quot; src=&quot;https://careers.duolingo.com/274c0c8ca00d7c576894.svg&quot; alt=&quot;icon-brain-16px&quot; width=&quot;17&quot; data-is360=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; You will...&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate on software projects with product design and backend aspects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop, release, and maintain native Android application features in Kotlin&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mentor and set technical direction for junior engineers on the team&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
